2007 Harley Davidson Heritage Softail Classic
Firefighters Special Edition - RARE & LOADED -

** Only 14,818 miles **
-Recently had a 15k service at Harley Dealership. 
-New battery 2 years ago
-Twin Cam 96B 1584 cc Engine. 
-Fuel Injected 
-6 speed 
-Vance and Hines Long Shot Pipes.  Sounds and looks amazing!!
-LED Headlights 
-Upgraded preimum seats
-Battery Tender 
-Harley branded Bike Cover 
-Premium Matching chrome diamond plate grips, pedals  footrests, and highway rests 
-Chrome Engine Guard 
-Leather bags in great condition and have support frames inside to hold shape
-Matching leather storage pouch on right side 
-New tires 2-3 years ago.
-Front windshield with built-in speakers 
-Battery tender 
-Trickle charge harness for battery charging or use for phone charger.

Paint and chrome are in great shape.  Garaged and driven rarely.  This is ready to be driven and enjoyed.
